 school and watch meeting for Friday evening in the Methodist church Also the Odd Fellows and Rebekahs oyster supper on Saturday night Also the cantata at the Methodist church on Sunday evening 4i thA Vnrmfirs Institute in town iuov vv mini hi ii i q hall on Monday and Tuesday Jan d and 4 On Thursday night of this week there is to be a school party in the town hall at which all former pupils are invited The next Grange meeting will be held all day Jan 15 in the town hall at which time there will be the instal lation of the new officers Mrs J F Babcock received word of the birth of a little daugnier on uec 6 to Mrs Cora Drake Bassett and husband at Chicago Mrs Jessie Peebles of Seville spent Monday here at Urant moseys aim Mrs Tvman Chidseys The Y M C A boys met last week Wednesday evening in the basement of Church of Christ and reorganized for the year They will meet there each Wednesday"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:19:41.701Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84028262/1920-12-31/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_himilco_ver01:data:sn84028262:00296026992:1920123101:0475/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=439&w=291", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_himilco_ver01:data:sn84028262:00296026992:1920123101:0475/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=878&w=582", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_himilco_ver01/data/sn84028262/00296026992/1920123101/0475.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["ohio", "united states", "medina", "medina county"], "location_city": ["medina"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["medina"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"